{"tid":107591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蒙古民眾捐馬匹、珠寶、存款　助國家還265億元債務","createTime":"2017-02-04T14:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T05:54:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e5b8a730d933dd9edb7ad82679e06499987dcc1","tid":107591,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>蒙古民眾捐馬匹、珠寶、存款　助國家還265億元債務</strong><br />\n2017/02/04 11:38:00<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n受全球期貨大跌以及中國對礦產需求量減少的影響，蒙古在去年陷入嚴重經濟危機，今年3月，蒙古開發銀行（Development Bank of Mongolia）發行的<strong>8.5億美元</strong>（約新台幣265億元）<strong>債券即將到期</strong>，蒙古屆時恐還不出此巨額債務，現在已有國民捐出自己的存款、黃金、珠寶，甚至馬匹，協助國家還債。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.azureedge.net/newsimages/2017/02/04/798655-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.azureedge.net%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F798655-XXL.jpg&h=78cb5066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲圖為蒙古傳統體能運動競技節日「那達慕」。（圖／美聯社／達志影像）<br />\n<br />\n蒙古先天擁有豐富的礦產資源，2011年起吸引不少外國公司前往投資，帶動蒙古經濟迅速成長，但受到全球期貨價格大跌影響，中國對礦產需求量也減少，再加上蒙古政府開採礦產的政策紊亂，<strong>外資大舉逃離</strong>，導致蒙古債台高築，處於嚴重經濟危機，甚至已無法支付公務員或軍隊薪水，，蒙古貨幣圖格里克（Tugrik）也在去年大幅貶值25%。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報導，蒙古政府正就財務緊急援助問題，和中國及國際貨幣基金組織（IMF）談判，但投資人仍擔心，談判無法及時在債券到期以前完成，屆時國家仍籌不到這筆鉅額債務。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有企業團體和議員也籌到約1億圖格里克（約4萬650美元）現金捐款</span>，有蒙古經濟學者也捐出1億圖格里克、10匹馬和1枚金戒指，也有議員把自己3個月薪水都捐給國庫。<br />\n<br />\n蒙古英文日報《UB POST》報導，<strong>蒙古每個國民都必須參加捐款計畫</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，各年齡層捐助金額不一，8歲兒童捐1000圖格里克（約0.4美元），30歲以下民眾應捐2.2萬圖格里克（約9美元），而蒙古經濟學家建議50歲人士捐20萬圖格里克（約81美元）。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=221787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D221787&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=34f1102c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D221787&h=b1baf36d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=221787</a>"},{"pid":"daaf3fdd4cf4265387297596b6a7c36f1e1735d4","tid":107591,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b46d5e6a8ca70a37682066e02a0b230f68257a","tid":107591,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfd873d811a59a6910826e34f187526e3f22434","tid":107591,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c712484035be35a18569f069b746ab3e2648ae21","tid":107591,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T00:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa4867bf1e774def59434a01e9442e83b6f9e5a","tid":107591,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T01:33:52.000Z","msg":"邊個埋支那堆邊個死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dbea5a7d1cc35026281995274b7105db62da65d","tid":107591,"uid":80198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個埋支那堆邊個死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細路，睇多d新聞<br />\n<br />\n過去幾年個蒙古總統最反華<br />\n<br />\n岩岩見完達賴，結果中國唔同蒙古買礦，蒙古礦主血本無歸<br />\n<br />\n正因為得罪中國，先落得如此下場"},{"pid":"2f1a2031fbb42680f5f79ba934fb86c41c3e99b1","tid":107591,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blo